flexi-streams
======
This is the patched version of flexi-streams(created by weitz,http://weitz.de/flexi-streams/).

It enables gbk(cp936,gb2312) encoding support,so that drakma could use it reading gbk pages. 

PLEASE REMEMBER SET FOLLOWING LINES IN YOUR .gitconfig
-------------------------------------------------------
[core]
	autocrlf = false
-------------------------------------------------------
